title: Fantasy premier league 2015/16  v1.0
description: Fantasy premier league 2015/16 v1.0 - from a variety of teams choose the one you want to win in the championship. Control your team. Take part in an international football championship in this game for Android. Develop a winning strategy for your team. Select the team, place players on their positions, select a captain, etc. Buy promising players and sell those who didn't live up to your expectations. Closely monitor the results of your team in weekly matches and watch your opponents
